        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="main-title"><span>Approve</span> Your Order to Start Treatment</h1>
            
            <p class="description">
                Based on your consultation, your provider has recommended<br>
                a personalized GLP-1 prescription to support your weight<br>
                loss goals.
            </p>

            <div class="action-section">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Now it's your turn to take action:</h2>
                <p style="color: #4A4A4A; font-size: 16px;">
                    Review your plan, confirm your payment method, and<br>
                    approve your order so we can begin fulfillment.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="warning-box">
                Your order won't be processed until you approve<br>
                it. You'll only be charged once it's confirmed.
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= link %>" class="cta-button">Approve My Order</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-section">
            <h3 class="support-title">We're here for you every step of the way.</h3>
            <div class="support-grid">
                <p class="support-text">
                    If you have questions about what happens next or need help with scheduling, our support team is ready to assist.
                </p>
                <div class="support-contact">
                    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@metabolixmd.com">support@metabolixmd.com</a></p>
                    <p>Call or text us at: <a href="tel:+1555123456">(555) 123-4567</a></p>
                    <p>Visit our <a href="#">Help Center</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

